NDCODFAPI

編譯環境建立說明
---------------

編譯環境需求軟體套件:
libreoffice
libpng-devel
poco-devel = 1.9.0
libcap-progs
openssl-devel
nodejs


編譯流程
--------
編譯 NDCODFAPI 需要安裝 POCO lib 及 nodejs, 以下列出各自編譯的步驟：


編譯 POCO lib
=============
./configure
gmake -s
sudo gmake -s install


編譯 nodejs
===========
./configure
make
make install


編譯 NDCODFAPI
--------------

npm install -g jake
npm install -g npm

./autogen.sh
./configure --enable-slient-rules \
        --with-lokit-path=bundled/include \
        --with-lo-path=/opt/libreoffice \
	--with-poco-includes=/usr/local/include \
	--with-poco-libs=/usr/local/lib \
        --enable-debug --enable-ssl


啟動主程式
----------

建立 cache dir(只須執行一次):
sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/var/cache/loolwsd
sudo chown `whoami` /usr/local/var/cache/loolwsd

make run
